    "text": "Responsible Education Mitigating Options and Technical Extensions Act of 2021 or the REMOTE Act of 2021\n\nThis bill addresses the administration of certain Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) educational assistance benefits, including by authorizing the VA to waive certain enrollment verifications, exempting foreign educational institutions from certain requirements, and extending the time limitations on the use of educational assistance benefits."
